            <thetext>At the moment the playground application uses the setting &quot;qx.version&quot; to create a link to the API viewer. This may end up in an unreachable URL if the playground uses a version string for which no API viewer is available online.

E.g. we put the playground with version 0.8.2-pre online but there is no API viewer online with this specific version.</thetext>
